title: Freshman keeper comes up big in Mines 4-1 loss
text:
Freshman keeper comes up big in Mines 4-1 loss Alex Worland blanks Colorado offense in second half relief role POSTED: 06:00 PM MDT Oct 04, 2015 UPDATED: 10:54 PM MDT Oct 04, 2015 
SD Mines falls 4-1 to Colorado Mines, but bright spot is third string goalkeeper Alex Worland. He allowed zero goals in his second half of relief.
